{"tid":1948819,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"戲院關閉前半天票房71萬 田雞：唔少手足都有經濟壓力","createTime":"2020-03-29T08:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T02:21:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b5324a8b92ad8a2415c7d0e95ccac1cd0a1e424c","tid":1948819,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"香港政府為應對日益嚴峻的武漢肺炎疫情，昨日宣佈所有娛樂場所，包括戲院，由昨日下午6時起，必須關閉14日。戲院關閉前的半天營業，票房約有71萬，而前日整天的票房才不過78萬，顯然在新措施實施前，去戲院看戲的市民是比前天增加了少許。香港影視圈近乎停擺，近九成人沒工開，演藝人協會會長古天樂與電影幾大屬會最近頻頻開會，希望可以幫助業界。<br />\n<br />\n電影工作者總會會長田雞今日向《蘋果》透露，幾大電影屬會之前已經與各大電影公司老闆和政府開過會，希望可以振興電影工業，田雞表示：「而家都傾咗一啲方案出嚟，睇下政府可唔可以幫到我哋，大家當然希望疫情後可以喺香港開番多啲戲，同時又搞咗個跨部門培訓計劃，等同業員可以提高競爭力，電影業係越來越難經營，唔少手足都有經濟壓力。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200329/large/1585464109_c2bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200329%2Flarge%2F1585464109_c2bd.jpg&h=4db7090c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200329/AG7Y2AOEN3E7YCNMPCQLRUNK7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200329%2FAG7Y2AOEN3E7YCNMPCQLRUNK7Q%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe8ljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=27440d65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200329%2FAG7Y2AOEN3E7YCNMPCQLRUNK7Q%2F&h=b2b41754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200329/AG7Y2AOEN3E7YCNMPCQLRUNK7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"91827e7ecded65b4175af3760d0c283ee79c4dd3","tid":1948819,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"其實田雞係唔係黃？"},{"pid":"bc4bcfae73e968b5bf469a2e6bbd1be547917ff3","tid":1948819,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港政府為應對日益嚴峻的武漢肺炎疫情，昨日宣佈所有娛樂場所，包括戲院，由昨日下午6